    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造一支独特的团队！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3655d63405b94eb5ef32791a6a236a92.poster.avif?t=1764336617\" width=632 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3655d63405b94eb5ef32791a6a236a92.webm?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3655d63405b94eb5ef32791a6a236a92.mp4?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打造一支独特的团队！您将从列表中选择英雄，其中每个角色都有随机武器、种族和职业。所有这些都会产生大量的随机组合！你的选择很重要：在一支强大的队伍中，英雄们会互相补充。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创建一首歌谣</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/755854ec95f37688e691ef9fa8002688.poster.avif?t=1764336617\" width=632 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/755854ec95f37688e691ef9fa8002688.webm?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/755854ec95f37688e691ef9fa8002688.mp4?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏提供一个民谣创作系统。创建一首符合你的游戏风格并增强你的英雄团队的歌谣！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参与史诗般的战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3a8310039bb57db24f3f00017b1c05fe.poster.avif?t=1764336617\" width=632 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3a8310039bb57db24f3f00017b1c05fe.webm?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803580/extras/3a8310039bb57db24f3f00017b1c05fe.mp4?t=1764336617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>只有通过歌谣创作系统和果冻矮人增强的强大英雄组合才能在历史上留下印记！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以及:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16种职业<br></li><li>20种武器<br></li><li>6 种种族<br></li><li>100多首独特的歌谣歌词<br></li><li>7 种果冻侏儒<br></li><li>事件：宝箱、祭坛、动物和意外相遇<br></li><li>游戏模式：竞技场、英雄之路、与巨人战斗、训练<br></li><li>主动与被动玩法的结合<br></li><li>原创配乐和音效的注重</li></ul>",
